title: Fajita Chicken Tostada Salad
descriptions:
Fajita chicken, crisp greens, Spanish rice and beans, bell 
peppers, topped with fresh Pico de Gallo, cheddar & Jack cheeses, guacamole and sour cream. Served in a tortilla 
tostada bowl with a spicy chipotle ranch dressing and 
picante salsa

title: Char-Grilled Chicken Caesar Salad
descriptions:
Char-grilled chicken breast, parmesan cheese 
and croutons served atop crisp romaine lettuce, 
tossed with our homemade caesar dressing.
